| 		             | <<OpenESB>>	| <<ServiceMix>> |
*--------------------+--------------*----------------*
| <<Glassfish v2>>   | Sun Jdk ORB / Glassfish ORB | Sun Jdk ORB / Glassfish ORB  |
*--------------------+--------------*----------------*
| <<Websphere v6.1>> | IBM ORB      | IBM ORB        |
*--------------------+--------------*----------------*
| <<JBoss v4>> 	     | Jacorb       | Jacorb         |
*--------------------+--------------*----------------*
| <<Weblogic v10>> 	 | Sun Jdk ORB / Glassfish ORB  | Sun Jdk ORB / Glassfish ORB    |
